為佳。如果塞山卡啦線，塞來托？<br />\n6.時間 : 繁忙時間為佳 ，8點開始<br />\n7. 宗旨 ：a. 封經濟 b.保護支援路線 c. 帶出塞地鐵訊息俾身邊人，確保足夠人玩<br />\n<br />\n叫勿塞者，必踢. 有問題，搵 admin<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/saveHK613\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FsaveHK613&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMR9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=0ffa130d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/saveHK613</a><br />\n<br />\n轉至計劃移民巴</blockquote>"},{"pid":"10e56528ca083717c8654e04878e77e519c569f5","tid":1212950,"uid":85219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:45:10.000Z","msg":"去立法會啊"},{"pid":"dc5ff68d0b78b332aadbcbcdac3242a094bef263","tid":1212950,"uid":59333,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:46:00.000Z","msg":"樓主慘 又比人負 但冇人識駁你"},{"pid":"e77bed83cd1fe483ffbd764516b8e79ec16983f6","tid":1212950,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:46:48.000Z","msg":"你塞唔塞班廢中廢老都會照講<br />\n到依個時候仲理人點睇做乜？"},{"pid":"45ac87e18567665272ea57aa986e19eac62b7e1f","tid":1212950,"uid":115769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5245a42145b274e2834a4230f3232b157112aa0b","tid":1212950,"uid":236140,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:43:23.000Z","msg":"戰場只有一個，立法會！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:47:05.000Z","msg":"無錯"},{"pid":"ea93d3ecf95e0ecc4278a8da870f33c4565edb56","tid":1212950,"uid":115769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc5ff68d0b78b332aadbcbcdac3242a094bef263","tid":1212950,"uid":59333,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:46:00.000Z","msg":"樓主慘 又比人負 但冇人識駁你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:47:38.000Z","msg":"負咪負,可以當飯食"},{"pid":"66abc5a61bb1888de2cfe60bc97ecb75bf0963e5","tid":1212950,"uid":84511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:47:50.000Z","msg":"十點半二讀，唔好搞交通，即到立會，大家加油"},{"pid":"5b2ba449ca8f2c1c221d9bdda6c438c3261623d3","tid":1212950,"uid":115769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e77bed8